    <body>
        <p class="TableText">Opens the Pending Changes window pane, which displays files in the project that are pending check in (if the project is integrated with a source control application). In other words, you can use this window pane to see which files you have checked out, which files have been created but not yet added to source control, which files other users have checked out, and which files are out of date. For more information see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Source-Control/About-Source-Control.htm">About Source Control</MadCap:xref> and <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Source-Control/Linked-Topics/Viewing-Files.htm">Viewing Files that are Checked Out or Modified</MadCap:xref>.&#160;</p>
    </body>
</html>